<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>AquaHealth AI - Water-Borne Disease Prediction System</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.0/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.4.0/css/all.min.css">
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
</head>
<body>
    <!-- Navigation -->
    <nav class="navbar navbar-expand-lg navbar-light sticky-top glass-nav">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <a class="navbar-brand fw-bold" href="#home">
                <i class="fas fa-water"></i> AquaHealth AI
            </a>
            <button class="navbar-toggler" type="button" data-bs-toggle="collapse" data-bs-target="#navbarNav">
                <span class="navbar-toggler-icon"></span>
            </button>
            <div class="collapse navbar-collapse" id="navbarNav">
                <ul class="navbar-nav ms-auto">
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#home">Home</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#about">About</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#prediction">Prediction</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#dashboard">Dashboard</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#alerts">Alerts</a></li>
                    <li class="nav-item"><a class="nav-link" href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
                </ul>
                <div class="ms-3 d-flex gap-2">
                    <button class="btn btn-sm search-btn" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" title="Search">
                        <i class="fas fa-search"></i>
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-sm notification-btn" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" title="Notifications">
                        <i class="fas fa-bell"></i>
                        <span class="notification-badge">3</span>
                    </button>
                    <button class="btn btn-sm theme-toggle" id="themeToggle" data-bs-toggle="tooltip" title="Toggle Theme">
                        <i class="fas fa-moon"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </nav>

    <!-- Home Section -->
    <section id="home" class="hero-section">
        <div class="animated-background">
            <div class="wave wave1"></div>
            <div class="wave wave2"></div>
            <div class="wave wave3"></div>
        </div>
        <div class="floating-icons">
            <div class="float-icon"><i class="fas fa-dna"></i></div>
            <div class="float-icon"><i class="fas fa-virus"></i></div>
            <div class="float-icon"><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i></div>
        </div>

        <div class="container h-100 d-flex align-items-center">
            <div class="row w-100 align-items-center">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="hero-content">
                        <h1 class="hero-title animate-fade-in">
                            AI-Powered Water-Borne Disease Prediction & Early Warning System
                        </h1>
                        <p class="hero-subtitle animate-fade-in-delay">
                            Predict water-borne disease outbreaks using advanced AI and real-time water quality analysis. Protect your community with data-driven insights.
                        </p>
                        <div class="hero-buttons mt-4">
                            <button class="btn btn-primary btn-lg gradient-btn me-3" data-bs-toggle="modal" data-bs-target="#predictionModal">
                                <i class="fas fa-flask-vial"></i> Predict Disease
                            </button>
                            <a href="#dashboard" class="btn btn-outline-primary btn-lg">
                                <i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> View Dashboard
                            </a>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="hero-illustration">
                        <div class="illustration-box">
                            <i class="fas fa-brain"></i>
                            <div class="pulse"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section id="about" class="about-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="section-title">About AquaHealth AI</h2>
                <div class="title-underline"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="row mb-5">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card about-card">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Problem Statement</h3>
                        <p>Water-borne diseases affect millions globally. Traditional detection methods are slow and reactive. We need proactive, AI-driven solutions for early outbreak prediction.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card about-card">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-target"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Aim & Objectives</h3>
                        <p>To develop an intelligent prediction system that identifies high-risk areas before disease outbreaks occur, enabling preventive public health interventions.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row mb-5">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card about-card">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Mission</h3>
                        <p>Empower communities with AI-driven water quality monitoring and disease prediction to save lives and ensure safe drinking water for all.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card about-card">
                        <div class="card-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-eye"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h3>Vision</h3>
                        <p>A world where water-borne diseases are predicted and prevented before they impact communities, through intelligent AI technology and data science.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-card text-center">
                        <div class="benefit-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-rocket"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4>Real-Time Analysis</h4>
                        <p>Instant water quality assessment and disease risk prediction</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-card text-center">
                        <div class="benefit-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-alt"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4>Early Warning</h4>
                        <p>Alert systems 48+ hours before potential outbreaks</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-md-4">
                    <div class="benefit-card text-center">
                        <div class="benefit-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h4>Data Insights</h4>
                        <p>Comprehensive analytics and trend analysis</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Prediction Section -->
    <section id="prediction" class="prediction-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="section-title">Disease Prediction</h2>
                <div class="title-underline"></div>
                <p class="section-subtitle">Enter water quality parameters for AI-powered risk assessment</p>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card prediction-form-card">
                        <h4 class="mb-4"><i class="fas fa-flask-vial"></i> Water Quality Parameters</h4>
                        <form id="predictionForm">
                            <div class="row mb-3">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">pH Level (0-14)</label>
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control glass-input" id="ph" min="0" max="14" step="0.1" placeholder="7.0" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">Turbidity (NTU)</label>
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control glass-input" id="turbidity" min="0" step="0.1" placeholder="1.0" required>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="row mb-3">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">Temperature (°C)</label>
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control glass-input" id="temperature" step="0.1" placeholder="25" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">Dissolved Oxygen (mg/L)</label>
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control glass-input" id="oxygen" min="0" step="0.1" placeholder="7.0" required>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="row mb-3">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">Population Density (per km²)</label>
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control glass-input" id="population" min="0" step="1" placeholder="5000" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">Recent Cases (count)</label>
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control glass-input" id="cases" min="0" step="1" placeholder="0" required>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="row mb-3">
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">Rainfall (mm)</label>
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control glass-input" id="rainfall" min="0" step="0.1" placeholder="10" required>
                                </div>
                                <div class="col-md-6">
                                    <label class="form-label">Sanitation Level (0-100)</label>
                                    <input type="number" class="form-control glass-input" id="sanitation" min="0" max="100" step="1" placeholder="75" required>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <button type="submit" class="btn btn-primary w-100 gradient-btn mt-4">
                                <i class="fas fa-magic"></i> Predict Risk Level
                            </button>
                        </form>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div id="resultContainer" style="display:none;">
                        <div class="glass-card result-card">
                            <div class="text-center mb-4">
                                <h4>Prediction Result</h4>
                                <div id="riskGauge" class="risk-gauge">
                                    <svg width="200" height="200" viewBox="0 0 200 200">
                                        <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" fill="none" stroke="#e0e0e0" stroke-width="20"/>
                                        <circle cx="100" cy="100" r="80" fill="none" stroke="url(#gradient)" stroke-width="20" id="gaugeCircle"/>
                                        <defs>
                                            <linearGradient id="gradient" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                                                <stop offset="0%" style="stop-color:#1abc9c;stop-opacity:1" />
                                                <stop offset="50%" style="stop-color:#f39c12;stop-opacity:1" />
                                                <stop offset="100%" style="stop-color:#e74c3c;stop-opacity:1" />
                                            </linearGradient>
                                        </defs>
                                    </svg>
                                    <div class="gauge-text">
                                        <div id="riskPercentage" class="risk-percentage">0%</div>
                                        <div id="riskLevel" class="risk-level">--</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="result-details">
                                <div class="detail-item">
                                    <span class="detail-label">Disease Risk:</span>
                                    <span id="diseaseRisk" class="detail-value risk-high">--</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="detail-item">
                                    <span class="detail-label">Confidence:</span>
                                    <span id="confidence" class="detail-value">--</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="detail-item">
                                    <span class="detail-label">Primary Disease:</span>
                                    <span id="primaryDisease" class="detail-value">--</span>
                                </div>
                                <div class="detail-item">
                                    <span class="detail-label">Secondary Disease:</span>
                                    <span id="secondaryDisease" class="detail-value">--</span>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="recommended-action mt-4 p-3 glass-card" style="background: rgba(52, 211, 153, 0.1); border-left: 4px solid #22c55e;">
                                <h6><i class="fas fa-check-circle" style="color: #22c55e;"></i> Recommended Action</h6>
                                <p id="recommendedAction" class="mb-0">--</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <div id="noResultContainer">
                        <div class="glass-card text-center p-5">
                            <i class="fas fa-info-circle" style="font-size: 3rem; color: #3b82f6; margin-bottom: 1rem;"></i>
                            <h5>Enter Parameters to Get Started</h5>
                            <p class="text-muted">Fill in the water quality parameters on the left to receive an AI-powered disease risk prediction.</p>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Dashboard Section -->
    <section id="dashboard" class="dashboard-section py-5">
        <div class="container-fluid">
            <div class="section-header text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="section-title">Dashboard</h2>
                <div class="title-underline"></div>
            </div>

            <!-- KPI Cards -->
            <div class="row mb-4">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-3">
                    <div class="glass-card kpi-card">
                        <div class="kpi-icon" style="color: #ef4444;">
                            <i class="fas fa-virus"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="kpi-content">
                            <div class="kpi-label">Total Cases</div>
                            <div class="kpi-value counter" data-target="1247">0</div>
                            <div class="kpi-trend" style="color: #ef4444;">
                                <i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i> 12% this week
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-3">
                    <div class="glass-card kpi-card">
                        <div class="kpi-icon" style="color: #22c55e;">
                            <i class="fas fa-check-circle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="kpi-content">
                            <div class="kpi-label">Safe Areas</div>
                            <div class="kpi-value counter" data-target="452">0</div>
                            <div class="kpi-trend" style="color: #22c55e;">
                                <i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i> 8% improvement
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-3">
                    <div class="glass-card kpi-card">
                        <div class="kpi-icon" style="color: #f59e0b;">
                            <i class="fas fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="kpi-content">
                            <div class="kpi-label">High Risk Areas</div>
                            <div class="kpi-value counter" data-target="127">0</div>
                            <div class="kpi-trend" style="color: #f59e0b;">
                                <i class="fas fa-arrow-down"></i> 5% decrease
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-3">
                    <div class="glass-card kpi-card">
                        <div class="kpi-icon" style="color: #3b82f6;">
                            <i class="fas fa-droplet"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div class="kpi-content">
                            <div class="kpi-label">Water Quality</div>
                            <div class="kpi-value counter" data-target="82">0</div>
                            <div class="kpi-trend" style="color: #3b82f6;">
                                <i class="fas fa-arrow-up"></i> 3% increase
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Charts Row 1 -->
            <div class="row mb-4">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card chart-card">
                        <h5 class="mb-4"><i class="fas fa-chart-line"></i> Disease Trend (Last 7 Days)</h5>
                        <canvas id="trendChart" height="80"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card chart-card">
                        <h5 class="mb-4"><i class="fas fa-chart-pie"></i> Disease Distribution</h5>
                        <canvas id="pieChart" height="80"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Charts Row 2 -->
            <div class="row mb-4">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card chart-card">
                        <h5 class="mb-4"><i class="fas fa-chart-bar"></i> Risk Level by Region</h5>
                        <canvas id="barChart" height="80"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card chart-card">
                        <h5 class="mb-4"><i class="fas fa-map"></i> Heatmap Data</h5>
                        <div id="heatmapContainer" class="heatmap-container">
                            <table class="heatmap-table">
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #34d399; opacity: 0.3;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #34d399; opacity: 0.5;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #fbbf24; opacity: 0.7;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #f87171;"></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #34d399; opacity: 0.4;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #fbbf24;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #f87171; opacity: 0.8;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #34d399; opacity: 0.6;"></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #fbbf24; opacity: 0.6;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #f87171;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #34d399;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #fbbf24; opacity: 0.9;"></td>
                                </tr>
                                <tr>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #f87171; opacity: 0.9;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #34d399; opacity: 0.7;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #fbbf24; opacity: 0.5;"></td>
                                    <td class="heat-cell" style="background: #34d399;"></td>
                                </tr>
                            </table>
                            <div class="heatmap-legend mt-3">
                                <span><span style="background: #34d399;"></span> Low Risk</span>
                                <span><span style="background: #fbbf24;"></span> Medium Risk</span>
                                <span><span style="background: #f87171;"></span> High Risk</span>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <!-- Recent Alerts -->
            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <div class="glass-card">
                        <h5 class="mb-4"><i class="fas fa-bell"></i> Recent Alerts</h5>
                        <div class="alerts-list">
                            <div class="alert-item alert-danger">
                                <div class="alert-icon"><i class="fas fa-exclamation-circle"></i></div>
                                <div class="alert-content">
                                    <h6>Cholera Outbreak Risk</h6>
                                    <p>Region: North Downtown - High contamination detected in water source</p>
                                    <small>2 hours ago</small>
                                </div>
                                <div class="alert-action">
                                    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-danger">View Details</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="alert-item alert-warning">
                                <div class="alert-icon"><i class="fas fa-triangle-exclamation"></i></div>
                                <div class="alert-content">
                                    <h6>Typhoid Risk Elevated</h6>
                                    <p>Region: East Valley - pH levels dropping, sanitation concerns</p>
                                    <small>5 hours ago</small>
                                </div>
                                <div class="alert-action">
                                    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-warning">View Details</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>

                            <div class="alert-item alert-info">
                                <div class="alert-icon"><i class="fas fa-info-circle"></i></div>
                                <div class="alert-content">
                                    <h6>Water Quality Improved</h6>
                                    <p>Region: South Beach - Treatment measures showing positive results</p>
                                    <small>12 hours ago</small>
                                </div>
                                <div class="alert-action">
                                    <button class="btn btn-sm btn-outline-info">View Details</button>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Analytics Section -->
    <section id="analytics" class="analytics-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="section-title">AI Analytics</h2>
                <div class="title-underline"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="row mb-4">
                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="glass-card analytics-card">
                        <div class="analytics-metric">
                            <div class="metric-value">94.8%</div>
                            <div class="metric-label">Prediction Accuracy</div>
                            <div class="progress mt-3">
                                <div class="progress-bar" style="width: 94.8%"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="glass-card analytics-card">
                        <div class="analytics-metric">
                            <div class="metric-value">91.2%</div>
                            <div class="metric-label">Model Performance</div>
                            <div class="progress mt-3">
                                <div class="progress-bar" style="width: 91.2%"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-4">
                    <div class="glass-card analytics-card">
                        <div class="analytics-metric">
                            <div class="metric-value">87.5%</div>
                            <div class="metric-label">Data Reliability</div>
                            <div class="progress mt-3">
                                <div class="progress-bar" style="width: 87.5%"></div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row mb-4">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card">
                        <h5 class="mb-4"><i class="fas fa-brain"></i> Feature Importance</h5>
                        <canvas id="featureChart" height="80"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card">
                        <h5 class="mb-4"><i class="fas fa-lightbulb"></i> AI Insights</h5>
                        <div class="insights-list">
                            <div class="insight-item">
                                <div class="insight-icon"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></div>
                                <div class="insight-text">
                                    <strong>pH Levels:</strong> Most critical indicator with 24% importance
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="insight-item">
                                <div class="insight-icon"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></div>
                                <div class="insight-text">
                                    <strong>Rainfall:</strong> Significant predictor (18% importance)
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="insight-item">
                                <div class="insight-icon"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></div>
                                <div class="insight-text">
                                    <strong>Population Density:</strong> 16% impact on predictions
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="insight-item">
                                <div class="insight-icon"><i class="fas fa-check"></i></div>
                                <div class="insight-text">
                                    <strong>Sanitation:</strong> Inverse correlation shows 15% importance
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <div class="glass-card">
                        <h5 class="mb-4"><i class="fas fa-history"></i> Historical Analysis</h5>
                        <canvas id="historicalChart" height="80"></canvas>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Emergency Alerts Section -->
    <section id="alerts" class="alerts-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="section-title">Emergency Alerts</h2>
                <div class="title-underline"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="row mb-4">
                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card alert-card alert-card-danger">
                        <div class="alert-card-header">
                            <i class="fas fa-map-pin"></i> High Risk Locations
                        </div>
                        <div class="alert-card-body">
                            <div class="risk-location">
                                <h6><i class="fas fa-location-dot" style="color: #ef4444;"></i> North Downtown District</h6>
                                <p>Risk Level: <span class="badge bg-danger">CRITICAL</span></p>
                                <p class="small">Contamination: Cholera - E.Coli detected</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="risk-location">
                                <h6><i class="fas fa-location-dot" style="color: #f97316;"></i> East Valley Region</h6>
                                <p>Risk Level: <span class="badge bg-warning">HIGH</span></p>
                                <p class="small">Contamination: Typhoid suspected</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="risk-location">
                                <h6><i class="fas fa-location-dot" style="color: #eab308;"></i> Central Park Area</h6>
                                <p>Risk Level: <span class="badge bg-warning">MEDIUM</span></p>
                                <p class="small">Contamination: Viral indicators rising</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-lg-6">
                    <div class="glass-card alert-card alert-card-info">
                        <div class="alert-card-header">
                            <i class="fas fa-megaphone"></i> Early Warning Messages
                        </div>
                        <div class="alert-card-body">
                            <div class="warning-message">
                                <strong>⚠️ URGENT:</strong> Do not consume tap water in North Downtown without boiling
                            </div>
                            <div class="warning-message">
                                <strong>⚠️ WARNING:</strong> Use filtered water in East Valley - Treatment ongoing
                            </div>
                            <div class="warning-message">
                                <strong>ℹ️ INFO:</strong> South Beach water quality improving - Monitoring continues
                            </div>
                            <div class="warning-message">
                                <strong>✓ UPDATE:</strong> West Hills cleared - Safe to consume
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-lg-12">
                    <div class="glass-card">
                        <h5 class="mb-4"><i class="fas fa-heartbeat"></i> Prevention Tips & Emergency Contacts</h5>
                        <div class="row">
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <h6 class="mb-3">Prevention Measures:</h6>
                                <ul class="prevention-list">
                                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Boil water for 5-10 minutes before consumption</li>
                                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Use water purification tablets if available</li>
                                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Maintain proper hand hygiene</li>
                                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Use sanitized containers for water storage</li>
                                    <li><i class="fas fa-check"></i> Avoid swimming in contaminated areas</li>
                                </ul>
                            </div>
                            <div class="col-lg-6">
                                <h6 class="mb-3">Emergency Contacts:</h6>
                                <div class="contact-box">
                                    <p><i class="fas fa-phone"></i> <strong>Emergency Hotline:</strong> 1-800-HEALTH-1</p>
                                    <p><i class="fas fa-envelope"></i> <strong>Email:</strong> emergency@aquahealth.ai</p>
                                    <p><i class="fas fa-hospital"></i> <strong>Nearest Hospital:</strong> City Medical Center</p>
                                    <p><i class="fas fa-water"></i> <strong>Water Authority:</strong> 1-800-WATER-SOS</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- Prevention Section -->
    <section id="prevention" class="prevention-section py-5">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="section-header text-center mb-5">
                <h2 class="section-title">Prevention & Wellness</h2>
                <div class="title-underline"></div>
            </div>

            <div class="row">
                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="glass-card prevention-card">
                        <div class="prevention-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-droplet"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5>Safe Drinking Water</h5>
                        <p>Use filtered water, boil before consumption, and ensure proper storage in clean containers.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="glass-card prevention-card">
                        <div class="prevention-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-soap"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5>Hygiene Practices</h5>
                        <p>Wash hands regularly with soap and clean water, especially before eating and after using restrooms.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="glass-card prevention-card">
                        <div class="prevention-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-flask"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5>Water Purification</h5>
                        <p>Install RO filters, use UV sterilization, or boiling methods. Chlorination also effective.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="glass-card prevention-card">
                        <div class="prevention-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-syringe"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5>Vaccination</h5>
                        <p>Get vaccinated against Typhoid, Cholera, and other water-borne diseases when recommended.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="glass-card prevention-card">
                        <div class="prevention-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-users"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5>Community Awareness</h5>
                        <p>Educate communities about water safety, hygiene, and disease prevention programs.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="col-md-6 col-lg-3 mb-4">
                    <div class="glass-card prevention-card">
                        <div class="prevention-icon">
                            <i class="fas fa-shield-virus"></i>
                        </div>
                        <h5>Immunity Building</h5>
                        <p>Maintain good nutrition, exercise regularly, and keep your immune system strong.</p>
                        <a href="#" class="learn-more">Learn More <i class="fas fa-arrow-right"></i></a>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

